 Transferring Logins to a Database Mirror 
	 August 13, 2010 
	 by  SQLSoldier 
	 SQL Server 
	 33 Comments 
	 0 
 


 I recently discovered that my book ( Pro SQL Server 2008 Mirroring ) has an older version of the script to copy logins to the mirror partner for database mirroring. The final version of the script handles SQL logins as well as Windows groups and users. I’m really disappointed that the newer script didn’t make it into the book because I put a lot of work into it to make sure it handled SQL logins. There are two main issues with transferring SQL 